      '<strong>Holder-Rewards</strong> — bei aktivierten Steuern starten Verteilungen ca. eine Stunde nach Launch und hängen vom Volumen ab.',
    ],
    pump_video_h: 'Im Video ansehen',
    pump_video_iframe_title: 'stonks.pump-Launchpad-Walkthrough',
    pump_docs_hint_html: 'Vollständige offizielle Dokumentation — <a href="' + STONKS_PUMP_DOCS + '" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stonks.pump-Manual</a>.',
    why_h: 'Warum es für das TON-Ökosystem wichtig ist',
    why_p1: 'sTONks senkt die Einstiegshürde für ernsthafte On-Chain-Projekte, nicht nur Memecoins. Wer einen Telegram-Account und ein TON-Wallet hat, kann ein echtes Produkt deployen, mit on-chain gelockten Tokenomics tokenisieren und ein Publikum erreichen, das bereits handelt. Das passt zur TON-Philosophie — die Blockchain ist direkt in Telegram integriert.',
    why_p2: 'Für Trader ist das Value-Prop einfacher: Jeder Token auf sTONks kommt mit einer verifizierbaren Verbindung zu echtem Code. Weniger LARP, mehr Signal.',
    next_h: 'Wie geht es weiter',
    next_site: 'die offizielle sTONks-Plattform',
    next_pump: 'der stonks.pump-Launcher',
    next_trader: 'das Trading-Terminal im Telegram-DM',
    next_chat: 'Community-Chat, in dem Launches in Echtzeit diskutiert werden',
    next_culo: 'Verfolge $CULO live',
    next_news: 'Aktuelle TON-Nachrichten',
    living_html: '<em>Diese Seite ist ein lebendiger Explainer, basierend auf öffentlichen Informationen von <a href="' + STONKS_SITE + '" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stonksbots.com</a> und dem <a href="' + STONKS_PUMP_DOCS + '" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stonks.pump-Manual</a>. Wenn du einen Fakt entdeckst, der korrigiert werden muss, schick uns einen Tipp im <a href="https://t.me/culoton" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CuloTon Telegram</a>.</em>',
    breadcrumb_news: 'Nachrichten',
  },
};

const c = COPY[locale];
---

<Layout
  locale={locale}
  pathWithoutLocale="/stonks"
  title={c.title}
  description={c.meta}
>
  <article class="news-article stonks-article">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href={`/${locale}/`}>{c.breadcrumb_news}</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span>sTONks</span>
    </div>

    <header class="stonks-hero">
      <img class="stonks-logo" src="/stonks.jpg" alt="sTONks logo" width="120" height="120" />
      <div>
        <span class="stonks-kicker">{c.kicker}</span>
        <h1>{c.h1}</h1>
      </div>
    </header>

    <p class="article-summary" set:html={c.summary_html} />

    <div class="body">
      <h2>{c.what_h}</h2>
      <p>{c.what_p1}</p>
      <ol>
        {c.pipeline_li.map((item) => (<li set:html={item} />))}
      </ol>
      <p set:html={c.what_numbers_html} />

      <h2>{c.trade_h}</h2>
      <p>{c.trade_lead}</p>
      <ul>
        {c.trade_li_html.map((item) => (<li set:html={item} />))}
      </ul>

      <h2>{c.rwa_h}</h2>
      <p>{c.rwa_p1}</p>
      <p>{c.rwa_p2}</p>

      <h2>{c.origin_h}</h2>
      <p set:html={c.origin_p1_html} />
      <p>{c.origin_p2}</p>

      <h2 id="stonks-pump">{c.pump_h}</h2>
      <p set:html={c.pump_intro_html} />

      <h3>{c.pump_flow_h}</h3>
      <ol>
        {c.pump_flow_li_html.map((item) => (<li set:html={item} />))}
      </ol>

      <h3>{c.pump_modes_h}</h3>
      <div class="pump-modes">
        <div class="pump-mode">
          <h4>{c.pump_seed_h}</h4>
          <ul>
            {c.pump_seed_li_html.map((item) => (<li set:html={item} />))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pump-mode">
          <h4>{c.pump_virtual_h}</h4>
          <ul>
            {c.pump_virtual_li_html.map((item) => (<li set:html={item} />))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="hint" set:html={c.pump_modes_hint_html} />

      <h3>{c.pump_protect_h}</h3>
      <ul>
        {c.pump_protect_li_html.map((item) => (<li set:html={item} />))}
      </ul>

      <h3>{c.pump_video_h}</h3>
      <div class="video-wrap">
        <iframe
          src={YT_EMBED}
          title={c.pump_video_iframe_title}
          loading="lazy"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
          referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="hint" set:html={c.pump_docs_hint_html} />

      <h2>{c.why_h}</h2>
      <p>{c.why_p1}</p>
      <p>{c.why_p2}</p>

      <h2>{c.next_h}</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>🌐 <a href={STONKS_SITE} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stonksbots.com</a> — {c.next_site}.</li>
        <li>🚀 <a href={STONKS_PUMP_LAUNCH} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stonkslabs.com/launch/ton</a> — {c.next_pump}.</li>
        <li>🤖 <a href={STONKS_TRADER} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@stonks_sniper_bot</a> — {c.next_trader}.</li>
        <li>💬 <a href={TG_STONKSONTON} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">t.me/stonksonton</a> — {c.next_chat}.</li>
        <li>🟡 <a href={`/${locale}/culo`}>{c.next_culo}</a></li>
        <li>📰 <a href={`/${locale}/`}>{c.next_news}</a></li>
      </ul>

      <p set:html={c.living_html} />
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .stonks-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 22px;
    margin: 18px 0 14px;
  }
  .stonks-logo {
    width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 0;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .stonks-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .stonks-article h1 { margin: 0; }
  .pump-modes {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 14px 0 18px;
  }
  .pump-mode {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 16px 18px 14px;
    background: var(--bg-section, transparent);
  }
  .pump-mode h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent-hot, var(--accent));
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .pump-mode ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .pump-mode li { margin: 4px 0; }
  .pump-mode strong { color: var(--text); }
  .video-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    margin: 16px 0 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: #000;
  }
  .video-wrap iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }
  .hint {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-mute);
    margin: 6px 0 12px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .stonks-hero { gap: 14px; }
    .stonks-logo { width: 72px; height: 72px; }
    .pump-modes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
